  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图，展示FinTech网络里ARP协议的实际工作流程。场景是五台设备：四台终端电脑分别跑PaymentGateway、LedgerService这些微服务，中间通过一个Switch做AuthVault认证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora D",
        "Switch",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Switch作为AuthVault的载体，四台电脑都是FinTech的不同服务节点。我先把参与者列出来：A和D都是PaymentGateway，B是LedgerService，C是TransactionQueue，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora D",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "Computadora B",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "Computadora C",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但注意A在ARP阶段其实扮演的是FraudDetection角色发起请求，这是为了演示跨服务通信的场景。另外Switch一开始MAC表是空的，这个状态要标注出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "ARP",
        "MAC",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在Switch上方加一个Note，写\"Tabla MAC vacía\"。然后A作为FraudDetection发起ARP Request，目标是广播到AuthVault，这条消息先到Switch。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Note",
        "Computadora A",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "ARP Request",
        "Broadcast",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
