      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这条ARP Request需要明确标注源和目的：源是A的FraudDetection，目的是Broadcast到AuthVault。Switch收到后要在MAC表里学习A的MAC地址，对应端口1。",
      "elements_involved": [
