      "utterance": "已添加：A到S的ARP Request带上了Origen和Destino标注，Switch的Note更新为\"Aprende: Puerto 1 → MAC de A\"。接下来Switch要把这个ARP Request泛洪到其他端口？",
      "elements_involved": [
