      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了三条线：S到B和S到C都是ARP Request (FinTech_AuthVault)，S到D是ARP Request (FinTech_FraudDetection)。这里有个疑问——D也是PaymentGateway，为什么要标FraudDetection？",
